org.openimaj.util.array

Class IntArrayView

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.util.array.IntArrayView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable

    public class IntArrayView
extends Object
implements Cloneable
    A wrapper around a java int array that allows views onto the array to be created without the overhead of maintaining copies of the data.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
